{"tid":1992434,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新民黨替一女子提訴廣播處長 因監督港台不力涉公職人員行為失當","createTime":"2020-04-28T06:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T06:51:24.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6fa569c7625d2fd3710aca92a9ae3817b7be028a","tid":1992434,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T06:51:24.000Z","msg":"梁家榮遭女子私人起訴公職人員行為失當<br />\n28.04.2020 14:42<br />\n<br />\n一名女子以私人檢控方式起訴廣播處長梁家榮，干犯公職人員行為失當罪。女子由新民黨立法會議員容海恩和律師陳永良代表，早上向沙田裁判法院提交文件，指控梁家榮監督港台節目不力，控告他5項公職人員行為失當罪，涉及4個港台電視節目，案件有待法庭審閱文件後，再決定是否受理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283925&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1283925%26csid%3D261_341&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=c12b61be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283925&amp;csid=261_341</a>"}]}